sources.title: Lasso | Full Movie | Horror Thriller | Sean Patrick Flanery | Lindsey Morgan
sources.description:
For 100 years, stories have been told about a cult near Hackett Ranch where people have been kidnapped and never found. The owners of the ranch say they know nothing about it. Guess where this year's rodeo is?  Touring a small-town rodeo festival, a group are hunted down by bloodthirsty cowboys!
2017.  Stars: Sean Patrick Flanery, Lindsey Morgan, Andrew Jacobs

metadata.Plot: The thriller centers around Kit (Lindsey Morgan) character and Simon (Andrew Jacobs) as they navigate life working for a senior community center. Their lives are turned upside down when they find themselves fighting to stay alive against a group of psycho, bloodthirsty cowboys from the local rodeo.
